The paper deals with natural language processing and knowledge representation, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of neural networks for reasoning and generalization also falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of large-scale knowledge bases, which is a topic in database systems (cs.DB). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval, as it involves predicting relations between entities in text and knowledge bases (cs.IR).
